<PARAGRAPH>
The first known solo ascent of 
<REF ID="409.9" SEMCAT="mountain" SYNCAT="np-obj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="name" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="plain">Mount Erebus</REFEX>
<ALT-REFEX>
